CREATE TABLE IF NOT EXISTS `code_edhorongo` (
  `id` INT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
  `ehkod` VARCHAR(21) NOT NULL,
  `company_id` INT NOT NULL,
  `ehkod_name` VARCHAR(255),
  `ehkod_mu` VARCHAR(21),
  `ehkod_muid` INT,
  `ehkod_price` DECIMAL(18,2),
  `ehkod_size` VARCHAR(21),
  `ehkod_width` VARCHAR(21),
  `ehkod_date` DATE,
  `ehkod_slength` VARCHAR(21),
  `ehkod_swidth` VARCHAR(21),
  `ehkod_spec` VARCHAR(255),
  `ehkod_balance` INT,
  `ehkod_desc` VARCHAR(255),
  `ehkod_room` VARCHAR(21),
  `ehkod_holder` VARCHAR(21),
  `ehkod_tur` VARCHAR(1),
  `ehkod_bairshil` VARCHAR(21),
  `ehkod_negjtalbar` VARCHAR(1),
  `ehkod_zoriulalt` VARCHAR(255),
  `ehkod_type` VARCHAR(1),
  `ehkod_angilal` VARCHAR(1),
  UNIQUE KEY uniq_ehkod_company_id (`ehkod`, `company_id`)
) AUTO_INCREMENT=1;
